<h1>Careers</h1>

<p><b>Empower a World of Innovation and Discovery</b></p>

<div class="banner"><img src="images/careers_banner.jpg" border="0" alt="Careers" /></div>

<div class="intro">Welcome to SGI. From our corporate headquarters in Milpitas, California to our offices throughout the United States, we have opportunities for you. Whether our technology is being used to design and build safer cars and airplanes, discover new medications and oil reserves, help us to understand and better predict the weather, or entertain us with thrilling movie special effects, SGI systems and expertise are empowering a world of innovation and discovery. So what are you waiting for? Check out our extraordinary career opportunities!</div>

<div class="bodybox2 right9">
<h2>Opportunities</h2>
<div class="modsep"></div>
<br />
